<title>AMAZING GRACE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hehpihna mak agi a hawih,
 Gimthei kei ei hukdam;
 Albang mangsa ei mukit tai,
 Ka mitduk avak tai.

[V2]
 2. Hehpih na'n lauh ding ei hilh hi,
 Lauhna cheng a nawhmang;
 Ka gin apat deihum takin,
 Hehpihna chuh a lang.

[V3]
 3. Lauhna, sepgim leh thang lakah,
 Kei ka chieh dawk zotai;
 Ziechan chuh hehpih na'n ei tun,
 In le eitun ina.

[V4]
 4. Zie chun chung sunni bang vaka,
 Kumsawt tuol I len tieng;
 I gin tung sanga phat tamzaw,
 Pakna di'n nei tai tiu.

[V5]
 5. Mihiem lunggel a hung tawpa,
 Leisiet hinkhuo beih tieng;
 Kipahna lungmuonna hinkhuo,
 Van achun nei tang ka.</lyrics>
</song>